&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;*LIFT operates sites in Chicago, Los Angeles, DC, and New York. LIFT operates as a hybrid work environment. Accordingly, this role will be expected to work in the LA office approximately two days a week.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POSITION OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
